Support Us
DONATE
HCT is fully ran by volunteers. Your donation will help keep the arts alive in Haines City and the surrounding area. Donate today by clicking the button below.
CLICK HERE TO DONATE
ADVERTISE WITH US
Do you own a business and want to spread the word? Advertising with us has the potential of reaching more than 4,000 patrons! For more information, please email
[email protected]
.
SPONSORSHIPS
We have different levels of sponsorship which can help your business be seen by 10,000+ residents in the Polk County area. You logo will be featured in all production advertising, programs, our lobby television, and our photo backdrop in the lobby. For more information on sponsorhips, please email
[email protected]
.
